  <brief_title>Case Study: HAGL-lesion (HAGL:Humeral Avulsion Glenohumeral Ligament)</brief_title>
  <official_title>Arthroscopically Repair of the Anterior Instability of the Shoulder Due an HAGL - Lesion - A Case Serie</official_title>
  <sponsors>
    <lead_sponsor>
      <agency>Schulthess Klinik</agency>
